<div class="container_main">
    <div class="box_template_image">
        <img src="https://blogmedia.evbstatic.com/wp-content/uploads/wpmulti/sites/3/2017/02/17160524/social-media-walls-for-events.jpg" class="template_image_login" />
    </div>
    <div class="box_login">
        <div class="welcome_text">
            Bem vindo ao SM, preencha o formulário para realizar seu cadastro ou pressione o botão REALIZAR LOGIN para entrar em sua conta.
        </div>
        <form class="form-group">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Primeiro nome">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Sobrenome">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Email">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Senha">
            </div>
            <div class="form_buttons">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Cadastrar</button>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light">Realizar login</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

